flowchart TD
    A[Upload PDF] --> B[Extract Q&A, Generate Distractors, Store in DB]
    B --> C[User clicks Start Exam]
    C --> D[Server creates attempt, shuffles questions & options]
    D --> E[Client shows questions WITHOUT correct answers, timer starts 60 min]
    E --> F{Time expires or User submits}
    F -->|Time expires| G[Auto-submit answers]
    F -->|User clicks submit| H[Manual submit]
    G --> I[Server validates, grades, updates attempt]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Return score summary + review data with correct answers]
    J --> K[User sees result page]
    K --> L{Action}
    L -->|Re-Exam| C
    L -->|View History| M[Attempts list]